window.bookSummaryJSON = "Casper Decuir’s psychic gift allows her to communicate with spirits, all fine and good until one wakes her up in the middle of the night to demand her time as intermediary with the police. As the younger half of H&amp;C Investigations, she is tasked with finding an assassin who leaves no trace of his presence other than a corpse.<br><br>When a student at the Gifted Elite School is threatened, Casper’s first lead takes her to a shifter with a mysterious connection to the murder victim.<br><br>Whispers of Hailey Arquette’s heritage includes Vodou priestess, psychic, and all around pain in the butt. When a group of shifter assassins targets her partner, they must choose those worthy of trust and those most likely to betray them."; 
